Sentencas: We developed a nano-structured Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3 (SSC55) cathode from slurry dispersed nanoparticles using a planetary bead-milling method.
Titulo: Preparation of nano-structured cathode for protonic ceramic fuel cell by bead-milling method

Sentencas: In order to evaluate the cathode performance, the cathode resistances and the protonic ceramic fuel cell properties were examined using electrochemical cells with a BaCe0.6Zr0.2Y0.2O3 - delta electrolyte disk at intermediate temperatures.
Titulo: Preparation of nano-structured cathode for protonic ceramic fuel cell by bead-milling method

Sentencas: The cells with a milled SSC55 cathode showed lower cathode resistance and higher power density compared to those with the SSC55 cathode prepared from the conventional method.
Titulo: Preparation of nano-structured cathode for protonic ceramic fuel cell by bead-milling method

Sentencas: The improvement is attributed to an increase in the cathode reaction sites caused by the use of the smaller particles and a good adhesion to the electrolyte surface.
Titulo: Preparation of nano-structured cathode for protonic ceramic fuel cell by bead-milling method
